Help [[

os.setlocale (locale [, category])
----------------------------------

  Sets the current locale of the program. `locale` is a string specifying a
  locale; `category` is an optional string describing which category to
  change: `"all"`, `"collate"`, `"ctype"`, `"monetary"`, `"numeric"`, or
  `"time"`; the default category is `"all"`. The function returns the name of
  the new locale, or **nil** if the request cannot be honored.
]]
